<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.12">
<l>vāveṉṟu colliyeṉ kaiyaip piṭittu</l>
<l rend="indent">valiyavē  kātiṟ kaṭippai</l>
<l>nōvat tarikki luṉakkiṅ kiḻukkuṟṟeṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">kātukaḷ nontiṭuṅ killēṉ</l>
<l>nāvaṟ paḻaṅkoṇṭu vaittē ṉivaikāṇāy</l>
<l rend="indent">nampīmuṉ vañca makaḷaic</l>
<l>cāvappā luṇṭu cakaṭiṟap pāyntiṭṭa</l>
<l rend="indent">tāmō tarāviṅkē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If, saying “come” and grabbing my hand,</l>
<l>[you] forcefully place the earring</l>
<l rend="indent">so that there is injury to my ear,</l>
<l>what pain [will] you experience here?</l>
<l>[My] ears will hurt. I am unable [to bear it].</l>
<l>I have brought Jaumoon plum fruits. See them, O Nampi!</l>
<l>O Dāmodhara, who previously drank the milk</l>
<l>so that the deceitful woman died and lept to break the cart.</l>
<l>Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
